data.description: Don't miss this rare opportunity to own in Magnolia Estates! This beautiful, spacious home includes a Formal LR, Formal Dining, as well as a downstairs office with French doors. Featuring hardwoods throughout the main floor. The grand kitchen has an abundance of cabinets and storage with tile floors and granite counters, plus an eat-in kitchen. A grand family room with large windows and tons of natural light, laundry room, and powder half bath finish off the main floor. Upstairs, you will find hardwoods continued through the hallway, 3 great-sized secondary bedrooms, a full bath, plus the large primary suite with walk-in closet and primary bath with garden tub. Don't miss the French doors leading to the back deck, overlooking the spacious, fully fenced back yard. This is a must see! Close to shops, restaurants, and the lake!! Recent updates include: Roof -2019, mostly new windows -2021, HW heater -2023, garage door and opener -2022, freshly painted exterior -2023.
